flowchart TD
    Start([User visits app]) --> EnvCheck{supabaseClient.js<br>has valid env vars?}
    EnvCheck -->|No| SetupHint[Show setup hint]
    SetupHint --> End([Stop])

    EnvCheck -->|Yes| AuthGate{Has session?}
    AuthGate -->|No| AuthForm[Show Auth Form]
    AuthForm -->|Sign Up / Sign In| AuthGate

    AuthGate -->|Yes| RoleCheck{Profile role?}

    RoleCheck -->|unknown| UnknownGate[Show Request Access screen]
    UnknownGate -->|Admin promotes| RoleCheck

    RoleCheck -->|admin / member| BoardPage[Enter BoardPage]

    BoardPage --> Dashboard[Dashboard view]
    BoardPage --> Kanban[Kanban Board]
    BoardPage --> Gantt[Gantt Chart]
    BoardPage --> Sphere[3D Data Sphere]

    Kanban --> TaskOps[CRUD Tasks via Supabase]
    TaskOps --> Realtime[Realtime sync to all clients]
    Realtime --> Kanban

    Kanban --> DragDrop[Drag & Drop reorder]
    DragDrop --> Midpoint[midpoint calculation]
    Midpoint --> TaskOps

    TaskOps --> Labels[Manage Labels & Dependencies]
    TaskOps --> Export[Export: XLSX / PDF / CSV]
